  <div class="controls">
    <button onclick="prevQuestion()">‚¨ÖÔ∏è ‡¨™‡≠Ç‡¨∞‡≠ç‡¨¨ ‡¨™‡≠ç‡¨∞‡¨∂‡≠ç‡¨®</button>
    <button onclick="nextQuestion()">‡¨™‡¨∞‡¨¨‡¨∞‡≠ç‡¨§‡≠ç‡¨§‡≠Ä ‡¨™‡≠ç‡¨∞‡¨∂‡≠ç‡¨® ‚û°Ô∏è</button>
    <button onclick="finishExam()">‡¨Ö‡¨≠‡≠ç‡≠ü‡¨æ‡¨∏ ‡¨∂‡≠á‡¨∑</button>
  </div>

  <div class="status" id="status">‡¨ö‡≠á‡¨∑‡≠ç‡¨ü‡¨æ ‡¨ï‡¨∞‡¨æ‡¨Ø‡¨æ‡¨á‡¨õ‡¨ø : ‡≠¶ | ‡¨¨‡¨æ‡¨ï‡≠Ä : ‡≠¶</div>

  <div id="results">
    <h2 id="resultTitle"></h2>
    <p id="scoreDetails"></p>
    <p id="timeTaken"></p>
